<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset='utf-8'>
  <title>MadLibs</title>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css'>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Scars</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>Wanna know how I got these scars???</p>
        <p>My father was a @Model.GetWord("occupation") and a fiend.</p>
        <p>So one night, he goes off crazier than usual. Mommy gets the @Model.GetWord("thing") to @Model.GetWord("verb") herself.</p>
        <p>He doesn't like that. Not...one...bit. So, me watching, he takes the @Model.GetWord("thing") to her, laughing while he does it.</p>
        <p>He looks at me, and he says <em>"@Model.GetWord("question") so @Model.GetWord("adjective") !?"</em></p>
        <p>He comes at me with the @Model.GetWord("thing"), <em>"@Model.GetWord("question") so @Model.GetWord("adjective") !?"</em></p>
        <p><em>"Let's put a smile on that face!!"</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <img src="https://brobible.files.wordpress.com/2017/10/heath-ledger-joker-new-interviews-book.jpg?quality=90&w=626" alt="thejoker">
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
